des:
Uniflex Connect is a home automation platform for curtains and blinds. It's a solution that allows you to control your environment in a simple and elegant way.

Through the Connect Hub and the Uniflex Connect app, you can control and create scenes for your curtains and blinds.

By enabling the Uniflex Connect skill, you synchronize the devices and scenes created in the app with Alexa and gain even more freedom! Just say Alexa!

To get started, you'll need to connect Alexa to your Uniflex products by following these simple steps:

1. Download the "Uniflex Connect" app from your app store;
2. Register your account using an email address;
3. Sync your Connect Hub;
4. Set up your devices (curtains and blinds);
5. Create scenes for your devices;
6. Download the Amazon "Alexa" app from your app store;
7. Set up your Alexa device in the app;
8. Search for the "Uniflex Connect" skill in the Skills tab of the Alexa app;
9. Click "Enable To Use" and you'll be redirected to the "Uniflex Connect" app;
10. Authorize Alexa to access your devices.
11. Done! The setup is complete;

You don't need to open the Uniflex Connect app to control your home devices; just say: Alexa.

Try saying:
"Alexa, open the blinds"
"Alexa, close the curtains"
